    "body": "The issue here is that the 02:00 is not repeated, instead the repetition starts at 02:15 in the original example and continues to 02:30, 02:45, 03:00.  The repeated intervals should be 02:00, 02:15, 02:30, and 02:45 as you see in @jorisvandenbossche example.  It's almost as if it is 15-minute period ending times so I think those need to be adjusted back before any inference would work.\n"
