    "body": "Yep , it is a complex problem! I am working with energy data with a frequency of 15 minutes. By definition in the energy field, the value associated to the timestamp is the mean value of the 15 minutes before the timestamp. It is why I have 03:00 which is repeated and not 02:00. If you can do something, it will be great, but I can live with this problem.\n\nThank you for your answers\n"
